{
  "stem": "3952.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After 4:00, we went back to cheder until about 8:30, 9 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a long day, no time to play, no recreation time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, we had-- about 5 o'clock, we had a half an hour to play a little in the courtyard and eat something if we had what to eat, which wasn't the always the case.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a long, hard day, and when you came home, you were already very, very tired.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I don't remember ever having a toy or-- or a ball to play with.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, if we did play with a ball, which I liked-- I liked soccer-- we played with a-- we took two-- two socks, and we huddled them together and made a ball out of it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's how we played ball.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that was till about 10 years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When I was 10 years old, we went into the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Hungarians came in, and immediately my father-- the next day my father was fired from his job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was no-- nothing to live on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we moved into Sighet, which was about 20 kilometers from-- from the village we lived in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there again, cheder, school, cheder, school, cheder, school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it was Hungary, not Romania?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then it was Hungary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then it was already Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I remember an episode where the same teacher who-- because this-- this place, Sighet, was-- when I was born it was Romania, then it was Hungaria, then it was Hungary again, and Romania again.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the same teacher taught us in the Hungarian school, the same teacher that me in fifth class in the-- in the-- in the Romanian school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was one of the best students also-- always in the class.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
